---
By: Henry T. Hamblin
Locus:
  Page: 154
  Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Falsehood
---
Learning to be men and women of faith is like being trained as an athlete.
We have to be tested, and our training made more severe, so that our
strength and powers of endurance are increased progressively. ...Every time
of testing prepares us for greater adventures in faith.
